article.story: SMITHFIELD, R.I. -- — Daniel Rivera had 23 points and 11 rebounds to propel Bryant to a 77-72 victory over Maine on Thursday night. Earl Timberlake had 20 points on 8-for-11 shooting and seven rebounds for the Bulldogs (17-9, 9-2 America East Conference). Sherif Kenney totaled 15 points and seven boards. The Black Bears (11-14, 3-7) were led by AJ Lopez with 15 points. Jaden Clayton had 14 points and two steals. Kellen Tynes added 12 points and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
